Twin bombs kill 30 at pro-Kurdish rally in Turkish capital 
Published By: Reuters - Today 
ANKARA (Reuters) - At least 30 people were killed when twin explosions hit a rally of hundreds of pro-Kurdish and leftist activists outside ...
